 @@ -88,3 +112,5 @@
 - Parse/runtime ambiguity: keep all plausible candidates but mark `status: needs_review` with
 evidence.
 +- Fallback ladder ordering ambiguity: when priority
 +  is implicit, preserve source order and mark
 +  `status: needs_review` with evidence of ambiguous ranking.
 +- Overlapping route triggers: when multiple routes
 +  match the same trigger pattern, emit all candidates
 +  with `status: needs_review` and cross-reference IDs.
